description:
In episode 165, Jack and Miles are joined by comedian Erin Foley to discuss the conservative version of SNL called 'Live From Omaha,' Anthony Bourdain and suicide, more shenanigans from Scott Pruitt aka George Costanza, the G7 Summit in Quebec, a new algorithm from the army for ideal caffeine consumption, and more!
